OL,7,FPat Ward was kicked and stabbed before
OL,8,Fbeing stripped, dumped and left to die
OL,9,Fin an alleyway in Clogher in Co Tyrone
OL,10,Fin 2019.
OL,12,F28 year old Niall Cox was jailed for a
OL,13,Fminimum of 20 years in prison last
OL,14,FSeptember for the 30 year old's murder.
OL,16,FHis former partner Karen McDonald (37)
OL,17,Fwas sentenced to 10 years for helping
OL,18,Fremove the father of four's body from
OL,19,Fher McCrea Park home.
